00:02:06.510 --> 00:02:10.630
So if you figure that out, it's
about 40,000 miles an hour.

00:02:10.630 --> 00:02:14.420
So this is a picture of
approaching the dwarf planet

00:02:14.420 --> 00:02:17.410
at about a million
kilometers out.

00:02:17.410 --> 00:02:21.800
So the other interesting thing
about the New Horizons mission

00:02:21.800 --> 00:02:23.940
is it was-- because
it had to go so far,

00:02:23.940 --> 00:02:27.320
it was intended to be a
pretty simple mission.

00:02:27.320 --> 00:02:30.410
