not articulated,

00:02:30.410 --> 00:02:35.640
so you had to move the
spacecraft to view the planet.

00:02:35.640 --> 00:02:37.910
But that meant that you
couldn't view the planet

00:02:37.910 --> 00:02:40.740
and do communications because
you had to turn the spacecraft

00:02:40.740 --> 00:02:41.640
to do communication.

00:02:41.640 --> 00:02:46.110
So as they were
doing the flyby, they

00:02:46.110 --> 00:02:48.030
