00:13:32.230 --> 00:13:36.760
are really truly the
measurements from space that

00:13:36.760 --> 00:13:40.730
are really most uniquely showing
human presence on the planet.

00:13:40.730 --> 00:13:42.900
And that's the nighttime images.

